IN RAHAM ALL SETUP, THERE IS "netflix.yml" playbook which didn't work for me.
Mine actually worked, the corrected version below



MY PLAYBOOK BELOW

Vim neflix.yml

---
- hosts: all
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: install apache and git
      yum:
        name:
          - httpd
          - git
        state: present

    - name: start apache server
      service:
        name: httpd
        state: started
        enabled: yes

    - name: ensure web root is clean for git
      file:
        path: /var/www/html
        state: absent

    - name: create fresh web root
      file:
        path: /var/www/html
        state: directory
        mode: '0755'

    - name: git checkout netflix clone
      git:
        repo: "https://github.com/AdedolapoRaji/pwj-netflix-clone.git"
        dest: "/var/www/html"
        force: yes



